| !Run file for screen saver application

RMEnsure ZapRedraw 0.50 If "<Zap$Redraw>" <> "" Then RMLoad <Zap$Redraw>
RMEnsure ZapRedraw 0.50 Error The Matrix screen saver requires ZapRedraw 0.50 or later

Set BlankTask$Dir <Obey$Dir>
Set ScrSaver$Running Yes
WimpSlot -min 120K -max 240K
Run <BlankTask$Dir>.!RunImage %*0